<h2>Missions Convention 2013</h2><p class="eventtime">Sunday, January 20, 2013<span class='event-sep'>, </span><span class="eventTime"> 9:00 AM - Sunday, January 27, 2013, 12:00 PM</span></p><br/><b>Group:</b> Missions</p><p><b>Coordinator:</b> Bob Ward (<script type='text/javascript'>
